snippet.title: Asteidus - Pre alpha Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for our upcoming game Asteidus which is still in development and at this stage is still in early alpha.
Asteidus is online RPG which puts focus on story driven quests and a world of magical landscapes, rich with unique history and mythology a player can be a part of in player vs player combat opportunities.

For more information check our website:
https://www.asteidus.com/
